00:07:12.609 --> 00:07:22.890 align:middle line:90%


00:07:22.890 --> 00:07:26.970 align:middle line:84%
Cusco is 11,200
feet above sea level

00:07:26.970 --> 00:07:32.690 align:middle line:90%
